# ─── Open-Source Intelligence (OSINT) Suite Environment Configuration ───
# Copy or rename this file to `.env.osint` in your project root to activate live external OSINT API scraping.
# If these variables are not set or left as demo placeholders, the system automatically falls back
# to our high-fidelity, secure OSINT simulation engine to guarantee zero timeouts during live demos.

# 1. Censys Platform API (Required for live port/TLS/infrastructure scanning)
# Step-by-Step Acquisition:
#   1. Sign up for a free researcher account at https://search.censys.io/register
#   2. Navigate to My Account -> API Credentials (https://search.censys.io/account/api)
#   3. Copy your API ID and API Secret below:
# Format Example:
#   CENSYS_API_ID=8f8e8f8a-1234-4bc3-a612-887766554433 # (36-character UUID format or 32 hex chars) # ggignore
#   CENSYS_API_SECRET=A1b2C3d4E5f6G7h8I9j0K1l2M3n4O5p6 # (32 to 64 character alphanumeric secret) # ggignore
CENSYS_API_ID=your_censys_api_id_here # ggignore
CENSYS_API_SECRET=your_censys_api_secret_here # ggignore

# 2. Shodan Threat Intel API (Optional - CVE scores & banner verification)
# Step-by-Step Acquisition:
#   1. Create an account at https://account.shodan.io/register
#   2. Log into your dashboard and copy the 32-character API Key:
# Format Example:
#   SHODAN_API_KEY=a1B2c3D4e5F6g7H8i9J0k1L2m3N4o5P6 # (32-character alphanumeric string) # ggignore
SHODAN_API_KEY=your_shodan_api_key_here # ggignore

# 3. IPinfo Geolocation Token (Optional - High-precision ASN & geo markers)
# Step-by-Step Acquisition:
#   1. Sign up at https://ipinfo.io/signup
#   2. Copy your Access Token from https://ipinfo.io/account/token:
IPINFO_TOKEN=your_ipinfo_access_token_here # ggignore

# 4. OpSec Proxy Rotation Layer (Protects law enforcement network IP during active scans)
# Example: http://proxy-user:proxy-pass@rotation.investigations.gov:8080 or socks5://...
OPSEC_PROXY_URL= # ggignore

# 5. Celery & Redis Broker Configuration
CELERY_BROKER_URL=redis://localhost:6379/0
CELERY_RESULT_BACKEND=redis://localhost:6379/0
